<section class="story" id="story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="story-inner">
      <div class="story-eyebrow">The Origin</div>
      <h2>The old playbook was broken.<br />So we burned it.</h2>

      <div class="story-body">
        <p>
          Bought the standard "this is how you do it" lies for decades. Climbed the right ladders. 
          Made the expected moves. And then — the floor came out. The playbook delivered its verdict: 
          not enough. Never enough.
        </p>
        <p>
          That was the dark night of the soul. Not a metaphor. The real thing.
        </p>
        <p>
          What came out the other side wasn't a cleaned-up version of the old life. It was something 
          different entirely. A framework. Six levers that, when pulled together, build a life that 
          doesn't depend on a salary, a system, or someone else's permission.
        </p>
        <p>
          65 years old. Rebuilding everything in real time. Documenting every step. Not because 
          it makes a good story — because it might be the map someone else needs.
        </p>
        <p class="story-motto">
          Learn. Document. Share.<br />
          <span>That's not just the motto. That IS the business model.</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-note">
        The founder's real name isn't on this site. That's intentional. 
        The reader is the hero here — not the founder.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: var(--navy-light);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
  }

  .story-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gray-light);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-motto {
    font-size: 1.2rem !important;
    color: var(--white) !important;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem !important;
  }

  .story-motto span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--gray) !important;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
  }

  .story-note {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
